tool_description: This api is used to send messages to WhatsApp chat platform via API.  see details www.intobo.com
title: Intobo WhatsApp API

api_list.name: startInstance
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://intobo-whatsapp-api1.p.rapidapi.com/startInstance/{number_id}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "intobo-whatsapp-api1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
